content:
This version is a small Motos Factory preview.
This is the latest version of B3313 able to run on Mupen64+

General Changes:
 - The Mutant Toad jumpscare was introduced.
 - The RTC (real time clock) system was introduced. Now the game checks your system time and changes some areas based on the time.
 - You can now switch to Luigi in Big Boo's fortress by entering the double doors with the L in front of the mirror.

New Areas:
 - Motos Factory
 - Unsettling Maze
 - Scorched Tar Land
 - Blazing Bullet Factory
 - a prototype version of Stellar Tower
